      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·鴻鴈之什·003.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">沔水.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>沔彼流水，朝宗于海。鴥彼飛隼，載飛載止。
嗟我兄弟，邦人諸友。莫肯念亂，誰無父母？</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In large volume, those flowing waters,
Go to the court of the sea.
Rapid is that flying falcon,
Now soaring, now resting.
Alas! among my brethren,
My countrymen, my friends,
No one is willing to think of the prevailing disorder;
But who has not parents to suffer from it?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-hongyan-003__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
      <prop type="x-work-id">shijing</prop>
