      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·鴻鴈之什·003.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">沔水.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>沔彼流水，其流湯湯。鴥彼飛隼，載飛載揚。
念彼不蹟，載起載行。心之憂矣，不可弭忘。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In large volume, those flowing waters,
Roll on their swollen flood.
Rapid is that flying falcon,
Now soaring, now rising higher.
When I think of those lawless men,
Now I rise up, now I walk about.
The sorrow of my heart,
Cannot be repressed nor forgotten.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-hongyan-003__003__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
