      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·鴻鴈之什·003.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">沔水.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>鴥彼飛隼，率彼中陵。
民之訛言，寧莫之懲？我友敬矣，讒言其興。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Rapid is that flying falcon,
Yet he keeps along the middle of the height.
The talk of the people, --
Is there no means of stopping it?
If my friends would reverently watch over themselves,
Would slanderous speeches be made?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
